  "title": "Customer Services for Freight Forwarding",
  "description": "<p>Liaise with customers/carriers and agents for import &amp; export shipments</p>\n<p>Work out quotations for customers</p>\n<p>Import &amp; Export permit declaration and custom clearance</p>\n<p>Prepare documentation and summary for customers' daily shipments</p>\n<p>Issue invoice and costing</p>\n<p>Assist in ad-hoc duties assigned from time to time</p>\n<p>Requirements : -</p>\n<p>Customer oriented with good interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>Good written and oral communication skills</p>\n<p>Able to work independently</p>\n<p>Familiar with air/sea Import and Export across trade shipment will be added advantage</p>\n<p>Preferably 1 year relevant experience</p>\n<p>Fresh graduates are welcomed</p>",
